{"tid":1803494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓外交部：文在寅沒說「香港新疆事務都是中國內政」","createTime":"2019-12-30T08:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T08:46:46.000Z","uid":64922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2115d9118b5eb0498d969f1253fa4eb62ce115b0","tid":1803494,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南韓外交部澄清，總統文在寅上星期在北京與中國國家主席習近平會談時，沒有說過「香港及新疆事務都是中國內政」的言論。<br />\n<br />\n新華社等多間內地傳媒在當日的新聞稿表示，「韓方認為，無論香港事務還是涉及新疆的問題，都是中國的內政。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，南韓外交部昨日澄清中國政府單方面發表的說法，表示文在寅在聽取習近平涉及香港及新疆事務的談話後，表示大致是「已經聽清楚」的言論作為回應。對於中國外交部的發言，南韓政府人士表示，雙方已透過外交渠道溝通。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那口交部做假到屈別國總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae106311e937b2d307eb81fefb380ec7df313cc7","tid":1803494,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:46:38.000Z","msg":"韓國企硬！"},{"pid":"91e3b1a416db9ed737a28080812c16ee7f53543f","tid":1803494,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=8cbd4fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a><br />\n2. deadline 30/12 (成功)<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%